sequenceDiagram
    participant DeploySH as deploy.sh Container<br/>(UBI8 + oc CLI)
    participant K8sAPI as OpenShift API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant ODHOp as ODH Operator<br/>(KfDef Controller)
    participant Manifests as odh-manifests<br/>(file:// tarball)
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP + 9091/TCP OAuth
    participant AM as Alertmanager<br/>9093/TCP + 10443/TCP OAuth
    participant BBE as Blackbox Exporter<br/>9114/TCP TLS
    participant ClusterProm as Cluster Prometheus<br/>openshift-monitoring<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant Components as Platform Components<br/>(Dashboard, NBC, ModelMesh,<br/>DSPO, Model Controller)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant PD as PagerDuty API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DMS as Dead Man's Snitch<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant SMTP as SMTP Server<br/>STARTTLS

    Note over DeploySH,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Platform Deployment

    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: Create namespaces<br/>(redhat-ods-applications,<br/>redhat-ods-monitoring,<br/>rhods-notebooks)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: Check addon-managed-odh-catalog<br/>CatalogSource (env detection)
    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: oc apply KfDef CRs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>ODHOp: KfDef CR watch notification
    ODHOp->>Manifests: Read manifests from<br/>/opt/manifests/odh-manifests.tar.gz<br/>Protocol: file://
    ODHOp->>K8sAPI: Create component Deployments<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: oc apply monitoring stack<br/>(Prometheus, Alertmanager, Blackbox)
    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: oc apply network policies<br/>oc apply dashboard CRDs/ISVs<br/>oc apply RBAC bindings

    Note over Prom,ClusterProm: Flow 2: Prometheus Metrics Federation

    Prom->>ClusterProm: Federate HAProxy, pod,<br/>cluster metrics<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS (service CA)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    Prom->>Components: Scrape /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>No encryption<br/>Auth: None
    Prom->>BBE: Scrape probe results<br/>9114/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    BBE->>Components: Probe user-facing endpoints<br/>(dashboard :8443, spawner, DSPO)<br/>HTTPS/HTTP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)

    Note over Prom,SMTP: Flow 3: Alert Notification (Managed Service)

    Prom->>AM: Fire alert rules<br/>9093/TCP HTTP<br/>loopback<br/>Auth: None
    AM->>PD: Critical SLO alerts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Service Key
    AM->>SMTP: User notification emails<br/>Configurable port<br/>STARTTLS<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    AM->>DMS: Watchdog heartbeat<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: URL Token
